'''《爱疯了》'''（{{lang-en|'''''Like Crazy'''''}}）是一部2011年美国[[爱情片|浪漫]][[剧情片|剧情片]]，由[[德雷克·多雷穆斯|德雷克·多雷穆斯]]导演，[[安东·尤金|安东·尤金]]、[[菲丽希缇·琼斯|菲丽希缇·琼斯]]、[[詹妮佛·劳伦斯|詹妮佛·劳伦斯]]及[[阿莉克丝·金斯顿|阿莉克丝·金斯顿]]出演。电影获得了2011年[[圣丹斯电影节|圣丹斯电影节]]评审团大奖，<ref>{{cite news |title=Sundance: 2011 Festival Award Winners |author1=Jay A. Fernandez |author2=Daniel Miller |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/risky-business/sundance-2011-festival-award-winners-94340 |work=[[Hollywood_Reporter|Hollywood Reporter]] blog "Risky Business" |date=2011-01-29 |accessdate=2012-06-21 |archive-date=2011-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110130234239/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/blogs/risky-business/sundance-2011-festival-award-winners-94340 |dead-url=no }}</ref>并包括完全未经排练的对话。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8668333/Felicity-Jones-rising-star.html |title=Felicity Jones: rising star |work=The Daily Telegraph |date=2011-07-31 |accessdate=2011-11-17 |archive-date=2011-12-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111204005320/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/starsandstories/8668333/Felicity-Jones-rising-star.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

