==灵感==
《爱疯了》被描述为宽松地受导演[[德雷克·多雷穆斯|德雷克·多雷穆斯]]的真实生活经验启发。在一次对他出生于[[奥地利|奥地利]]的前妻Desiree Pappenscheller的采访时，她说电影是对她和德雷克·多雷穆斯爱情和婚姻历史的回放，包括她的美国移民问题。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.metro.us/newyork/entertainment/article/987932--like-crazy-based-on-a-true-story |title=‘Like Crazy’: Based on a true story? |last=Garrison |first=Cassandra |newspaper=[[Metro_New_York|Metro]] |date=2011-10-04 |accessdate=2011-10-04 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111012172712/http://www.metro.us/newyork/Entertainment/article/987932--like-crazy-based-on-a-true-story |archivedate=2011-10-12 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | last=Carrillo | first=Sarah | url=http://graphic.pepperdine.edu/news/2004/2004-08-30-stuckstudent.htm | title=Student's visa leaves her stuck in Austria | work=Graphic | publisher=[[Pepperdine_University|Pepperdine University]] | date=2004-08-30 | accessdate=2012-01-27 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120106144531/http://graphic.pepperdine.edu/news/2004/2004-08-30-stuckstudent.htm | archivedate=2012-01-06 }}</ref>

==制作==
《爱疯了》使用并不昂贵的[[佳能_EOS_7D|佳能 EOS 7D]]单镜头反光相机拍摄，且成本没有超过250,000美元。<ref name="Shot">{{cite web |url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/lff_11_drake_doremus_says_he_shot_like_crazy_for_250000_on_a_1500_stills_ca |title=Drake Doremus Says He Shot 'Like Crazy' For $250,000 On A $1,500 Still Camera |first=Oliver |last=Lyttelton |work=IndieWire |date=2011-10-26 |accessdate=2011-11-13 |archive-date=2011-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111126053844/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/lff_11_drake_doremus_says_he_shot_like_crazy_for_250000_on_a_1500_stills_ca |dead-url=no }}</ref>电影由Crispy Films拍摄，并被[[派拉蒙优势影业|派拉蒙优势影业]]及制作公司Indian Paintbrush组成的联合体购买。电影于2011年10月28日在美国上映。<ref name=littlething/>

安东和菲丽希缇在电影中担任主角。在拍摄之前他们在洛杉矶的一家墨西哥餐厅见面以互相了解。<ref name=littlething/>菲丽希缇告诉《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的史蒂文·泽奇克：“我记得我在想，‘我只是希望他是个好人’。”安东和菲丽希缇在拍摄电影之前参加了一个在没有剧本的情况下完成的排练部分。<ref name=littlething>{{cite web|last=Zeitchik|first=Steven|title=A 'crazy' little thing called love|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/oct/23/entertainment/la-ca-like-crazy-20111023|work=[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]|publisher=([[Tribune_Company|Tribune Company]])|accessdate=2012-06-11|date=2011-10-23|archive-date=2012-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120306154706/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/oct/23/entertainment/la-ca-like-crazy-20111023|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==评价==
《爱疯了》在[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上拥有73%“认证新鲜”的评价，评论认为“（《爱疯了》）拥有很多浪漫电影过分伤感的伏笔，但是《爱疯了》允许其角色在对话之外表达他们，构造了一个真实、亲密的作品。”<ref>{{rotten-tomatoes|like_crazy|Like Crazy}}</ref>电影是[[基督科学箴言报|基督科学箴言报]]2011年第三最佳的电影。<ref>{{cite web |first=Peter |last=Rainer |url=http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Movies/2011/1221/The-10-best-movies-of-2011/Like-Crazy |title=10 best movies of 2011 - 'Like Crazy' |publisher=[[基督科学箴言报|基督科学箴言报]] |date=2011-12-21 |accessdate=2012-01-27 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107185846/http://www.csmonitor.com/The-Culture/Movies/2011/1221/The-10-best-movies-of-2011/Like-Crazy |dead-url=no }}</ref>

电影于2012年1月在英国发行后，[[Philip_French|Philip French]]将其描述为“令人喜爱的、轻松的、酸甜的”和一部“更少刻意聪明的、更少娱乐化的《[[情留半天|情留半天]]》和《[[日落巴黎|日落巴黎]]》的组合”，在四或五年间展开。<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/jan/29/like-crazy-drake-doremus-review | title= Like Crazy – review | work= The Observer | date= 2012-01-28 | first= Philip | last= French | authorlink= Philip French | accessdate= 2012-01-30 | archive-date= 2012-01-30 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120130081352/http://www.guardian.co.uk/film/2012/jan/29/like-crazy-drake-doremus-review | dead-url= no }}</ref>

